{
  "stem": "24830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But a lot helped-- a lot helped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Especially there was a lot of-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] how do you call?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Minister, and priest, and people, even in the prefecture-- some of them were very willing to help.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, another-- oh, then, so I change my name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All of a sudden, I don't-- I didn't want to meet anybody I knew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because I was not Micheline Kaplan anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was Micheline Beaumont.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So one of my friend in school ask me if I have a place to-- to hide.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She said, why don't you come and live with us?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I came and lived with her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Jewish?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not-- no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If not, it wouldn't have been any need.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So one day, everything was nice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day, she told me, oh-- the mother told me, we know a family, and they need false paper.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they don't know where to get it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they didn't know I was in the underground.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't want them to know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it bother me, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know I could do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So finally, I went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I say, you know, I know somebody who could make false paper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I make false paper for them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a few days later, they asked me to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because it was too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In a way, I didn't blame them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, if you hide a Jewish person, you could be deported with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a very difficult thing to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So you got the-- when you got these papers for these-- for the people, where-- how did you go about doing that?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How did you get the papers?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What did you do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, so, when-- first we put them--",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
